                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17641212-40-off208 t17641212-40-cd209"></join>. +</p>
               <p>The prisoner had carried the said goods to pawn; but it appearing to be done under the direction of her husband, and the prosecutor giving her a good character,</p>
               <p>She was <rs id="t17641212-40-verdict210" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17641212-40-verdict210" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               Acquitted
            </rs>.</p>
